main event: A witness reported seeing bright, curved objects in the sky near Kaiden, Ohio on 12/26/200.
interesting points: The object appeared as a bright and curved object.
The observers were apparently unaware of what the object was.
The report includes a sketch showing the object's movement and position relative to the horizon and compass.
The witness described the object as moving slowly, stopping suddenly, and exhibiting erratic maneuvering.
